      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "description": "Per-peer BGP session uptime in seconds. Series drops to 0 (or vanishes) when a session goes down — the closest proxy to BGP peer state available from the dom-synth exporter. Real bgpPeerState (Idle/Active/Established/...) would require BGP4-MIB via snmp_exporter, currently out of scope.",
